sequenceDiagram
    participant Router as 模型路由器
    participant Classifier as complexity-classifier.ts
    participant Meta as TASK.md 元数据
    participant History as routing-history.ts 失败率

    Router->>Classifier: classifyUnit(unitType, unitId, budgetPct)
    Classifier->>Classifier: 查 UNIT_TYPE_TIERS 表得默认 tier
    alt unitType == "execute-task"
      Classifier->>Meta: extractTaskMetadata(unitId)
      Meta-->>Classifier: fileCount, depCount, keywords...
      Classifier->>Classifier: analyzeTaskComplexity() 上调 tier
    end
    Classifier->>History: getAdaptiveTierAdjustment(unitType, tier)
    History-->>Classifier: 历史高失败率 → 上调
    Classifier->>Classifier: applyBudgetPressure(budgetPct) 强制降级
    Classifier-->>Router: {tier: "standard", reason: "...", downgraded: false}